---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/accounting-zen/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="Tax Strategy | Zen Ledger Advisory"
  description="Precision tax strategy engagement — Zen Ledger Advisory's deep-dive service detail."
  active="services"
  canonicalPath="/templates/accounting-zen/services/tax-strategy"
>
<main class="mt-32">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="max-w-zl-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop mb-section-gap">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-end justify-between gap-gutter">
<div class="max-w-2xl">
<span class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-outline tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4 block">Service Detail / Tax Strategy</span>
<h1 class="font-zl-display text-zl-display mb-6">The Calculus of Restraint.</h1>
<p class="text-zl-body-lg font-zl-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                        Strategic tax optimization for international entities. We navigate the intricate intersections of global jurisdiction with surgical precision and quiet confidence.
                    </p>
</div>
<div class="hidden md:block pb-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-surface-tint text-6xl opacity-20">architecture</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="zen-line mt-12"></div>
</section>
<!-- Technical Visualization -->
<section class="max-w-zl-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop mb-section-gap">
<div class="canvas-frame aspect-video w-full bg-surface-container-lowest relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center technical-flow-bg">
<!-- SVG Diagram Simulation -->
<svg class="w-full h-full max-w-4xl opacity-80" fill="none" viewbox="0 0 800 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<!-- Global Entity Node -->
<rect height="40" stroke="#1b1c1c" stroke-width="0.5" width="100" x="350" y="50"></rect>
<text class="tracking-widest" fill="#1b1c1c" font-family="Inter" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" x="400" y="75">GLOBAL ENTITY</text>
<!-- Flows -->
<path d="M400 90 V140" stroke="#1b1c1c" stroke-dasharray="4 4" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
<!-- Middle Nodes -->
<rect height="40" stroke="#1b1c1c" stroke-width="0.5" width="120" x="150" y="140"></rect>
<text fill="#44474a" font-family="Inter" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" x="210" y="165">REGION A: COMPLIANCE</text>
<rect height="40" stroke="#1b1c1c" stroke-width="0.5" width="120" x="530" y="140"></rect>
<text fill="#44474a" font-family="Inter" font-size="9" text-anchor="middle" x="590" y="165">REGION B: OPTIMIZATION</text>
<!-- Cross-Flow Connectors -->
<path d="M400 140 L270 160" stroke="#1b1c1c" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
<path d="M400 140 L530 160" stroke="#1b1c1c" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
<!-- Resultant Logic -->
<circle cx="400" cy="280" r="40" stroke="#1b1c1c" stroke-width="0.5"></circle>
<text fill="#1b1c1c" font-family="Inter" font-size="8" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle" x="400" y="283">ZENITH</text>
<path d="M210 180 Q210 280 360 280" stroke="#c5c6ca" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
<path d="M590 180 Q590 280 440 280" stroke="#c5c6ca" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
<!-- Decorative Thin Elements -->
<line stroke="#efeded" stroke-width="1" x1="0" x2="800" y1="200" y2="200"></line>
</svg>
<!-- Floating Info -->
<div class="absolute bottom-8 right-8 text-right">
<p class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-outline uppercase tracking-tighter">FIG 1.0 // CAPITAL FLUX TOPOLOGY</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Bento Details Grid -->
<section class="max-w-zl-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop mb-section-gap">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter">
<!-- Large Card: Methodology -->
<div class="md:col-span-8 canvas-frame p-12 flex flex-col justify-between bg-surface-container-low transition-all hover:bg-surface-container duration-500">
<div>
<h3 class="font-zl-headline-md text-zl-headline-md mb-6">Methodology: The Silent Shift</h3>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant max-w-lg mb-8">
                            We do not pursue aggressive loopholes. Instead, we master the existing regulatory framework to ensure structural efficiency. Our approach is characterized by minimal movement and maximum impact, aligning your global footprint with regional incentives.
                        </p>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-12">
<div>
<span class="block text-zl-display font-zl-display text-primary">0.5pt</span>
<span class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-outline">PRECISION TOLERANCE</span>
</div>
<div>
<span class="block text-zl-display font-zl-display text-primary">100%</span>
<span class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-outline">COMPLIANCE RATIO</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Small Card: Global Reach -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 canvas-frame p-8 flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl">public</span>
<h3 class="font-zl-headline-md text-zl-headline-md">Jurisdictional Mastery</h3>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                        Operating across 45+ territories, managing multi-tier entity structures with seamless reporting.
                    </p>
<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-wide">
<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-primary"></span> European VAT Logic</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-primary"></span> APAC Growth Incentives</li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1 h-1 bg-primary"></span> North American Treaties</li>
</ul>
</div>
<!-- Three Small Info Cards -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 canvas-frame p-8 hover:border-primary transition-colors">
<h4 class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-outline uppercase mb-4">Phase 01</h4>
<p class="font-zl-headline-md text-zl-headline-md mb-2">Audit &amp; Analysis</p>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Deconstructing current structures to identify latent friction points.</p>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-4 canvas-frame p-8 hover:border-primary transition-colors">
<h4 class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-outline uppercase mb-4">Phase 02</h4>
<p class="font-zl-headline-md text-zl-headline-md mb-2">Structural Re-entry</p>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Redefining capital flow pathways with minimal operational disruption.</p>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-4 canvas-frame p-8 hover:border-primary transition-colors">
<h4 class="text-zl-label-sm font-zl-label-sm text-outline uppercase mb-4">Phase 03</h4>
<p class="font-zl-headline-md text-zl-headline-md mb-2">Ongoing Vigilance</p>
<p class="text-zl-body-md font-zl-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Continuous monitoring of policy shifts and adaptive re-calibration.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="bg-primary text-on-primary py-section-gap overflow-hidden relative">
<div class="max-w-zl-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop flex flex-col items-center text-center relative z-10">
<h2 class="font-zl-display text-zl-display mb-8">Ready for a dialogue on restraint?</h2>
<p class="text-zl-body-lg font-zl-body-lg mb-12 opacity-70 max-w-xl">
                    We invite you to a confidential consultation to explore how precision tax strategy can stabilize your international operations.
                </p>
<button class="px-12 py-4 border border-on-primary text-on-primary font-zl-label-sm text-zl-label-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] hover:bg-on-primary hover:text-primary transition-all duration-500">
                    Initiate Discussion
                </button>
</div>
<!-- Background abstraction -->
<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none">
<svg height="100%" preserveaspectratio="none" viewbox="0 0 1000 1000" width="100%">
<path d="M0 500 Q 250 200 500 500 T 1000 500" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
<path d="M0 600 Q 250 300 500 600 T 1000 600" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
<path d="M0 400 Q 250 100 500 400 T 1000 400" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
</svg>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</TemplateLayout>
